08:11.200 --> 08:14.067
-It's in that bag in there.

08:14.067 --> 08:15.100
-In which bag?

08:15.133 --> 08:16.400
-That bag on
the floorboard over there?

08:16.433 --> 08:17.767
-Actually, I don't know, man.

08:17.800 --> 08:19.200
-You don't know where
it's at in there?

08:19.233 --> 08:20.433
-No.

08:20.467 --> 08:22.100
-Well, did you put it in there?

08:22.133 --> 08:23.967
-Yes, sir. I mean,
it was a joint.

08:24.067 --> 08:25.967
