of pills there,

10:01.000 --> 10:02.733
there's Xanax in there,
and all kinds

10:02.767 --> 10:05.300
of different painkillers.

10:05.333 --> 10:10.033
Then there is, in a breath mint
box... in the 17 years
I've been doing this,

10:10.067 --> 10:13.767
I can't see I've ever ran across
anybody that had their marijuana
individually packaged,

10:13.800 --> 10:19.233
and each one of the packages
have individual prices
written on the bag.

10:19.267 --> 10:21.567
But I guess there's a first time
for everything.

10:21.600 --> 10:24.933
Hey, David, I know you said
this is your mom's backpack--

10:24.967 --> 10:26.700
-It's not my mom's backpack,
it's mine.

10:26.733 --> 10:30.000
