uses it from time to time...
-Okay...

10:30.033 --> 10:31.900
-to put her meds in?

10:31.933 --> 10:36.167
I'd forgotten to mention
the pills, and I-- that's--

10:36.200 --> 10:39.300
that was not something I--
-Do me a favor, put your hands
behind your back.

10:39.333 --> 10:42.167
Just stay seated.

10:42.200 --> 10:45.933
-He said he doesn't
have prior pill convictions.

10:45.967 --> 10:48.133
I-- I'm not trying to be...
a druggie right now,

10:48.167 --> 10:51.000
I'm really tryin' to take care
of a family that--

10:51.033 --> 10:54.033
-Well, I mean, if--
if you're trying to take care
of a family, why in the world

10:54.067 --> 10:57.100
would you have all that mess?
-Dude-- I-- I shoulda

10:57.133 --> 11:00.067
even thought
about cleaning it out
before I went anywhere,

11:00.067 --> 11:02.300
but-- dude--
-I know, but you put the stuff
in there.

11:02.333 --> 11:04.967
-Not all of it was put in there
by me, man.

11:05.067 --> 11:08.833
