drug free,

12:19.067 --> 12:21.800
but... I was just
playin' around, man.
-What do you mean,

12:21.833 --> 12:24.867
playin' around?
-I-- I thought that the--

12:24.900 --> 12:28.333
marijuana looked cool
in different bags?
-Sure.

12:28.367 --> 12:30.400
I was an idiot.

12:30.433 --> 12:32.933
-Okay, well, who-- who
were you gonna sell it to?

12:32.967 --> 12:37.733
-Nobody, sir.
