-Because I wanted to know

12:40.400 --> 12:43.467
how much they were worth, man.
-Well, who was gonna tell you
that they were worth that...

12:43.500 --> 12:49.533
when you made the price up?
-I mean-- I'm... not a drug...
seller or any of that--

12:49.567 --> 12:52.467
-I'm not saying that you are,
