19:35.300 --> 19:36.833
I don't know
if they have a litter box
or something,

19:36.867 --> 19:39.467
but... 'cause if the landlord
finds out...
they're gonna end up

19:39.500 --> 19:41.133
charging you a lot to try
to clean the place up,

19:41.167 --> 19:42.767
you know?
-I'll-- I'll clean it.

19:42.800 --> 19:45.367
-It's really bad.
So hopefully you can get
the help you need, all right?

19:45.400 --> 19:46.933
-Thank you.

19:46.967 --> 19:49.700
-132 and Bush,
I've got him at gunpoint.

19:49.733 --> 19:51.667
-Dispatcher:
Okay, gunpoint, 132 and Bush.

